{"tid":1674944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益］陳同佳點處理先？垃圾比卡超，讀多幾年書先啦","createTime":"2019-10-25T13:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T11:43:58.000Z","uid":188630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6bb98f594d50dde3608e74ca2da960eeb1ebd5c","tid":1674944,"uid":188630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:58:01.000Z","msg":"網上入台證申請唔倒其實好正常，一個普通市民都有機會申請唔倒，落地簽證根本好L正常，成班廢柴衝出來柒，<br />\n一個殺人犯隨時隨地網上簽證用遊客身分自出自入，佢話自首啫，一入境攞把槍周圍殺人咁點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果係一個瘋狂殺人犯，話自首就咁返來香港，比卡超俾唔俾佢入呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />柒婆唔好懶hi有初心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec3963ade88a7fefba1b8ef59052f2e9297997a","tid":1674944,"uid":188630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:58:24.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"4a98ad5a76338aafce3508a2e013aac069b890e4","tid":1674944,"uid":188630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"faa1a441e63bfb0e27694b22c72780d6d2095d08","tid":1674944,"uid":188630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"推 3/10"},{"pid":"38f209d61a2409a64b38477329bed136e61b3380","tid":1674944,"uid":188630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"推 4/10"},{"pid":"7a4e497dc3ef187b7563ce19c9d6a2cbd90c4f2a","tid":1674944,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:06:15.000Z","msg":"同英國個單撞死人一撚樣<br />\n搞到最後咪唔移送<br />\n3個月後蚊都訓啦<br />\n屌<br />\n鬼叫蔣公剿匪不力<br />\n依家習熊熊一中原則<br />\n永遠都係政治凌駕法律架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac